# Chat Application

This is a real-time chat application developed using React.js for the frontend and Node.js for the backend. Users can join a chat room and engage in real-time conversations.

## Table of Contents
- [Features](#features)
- [Requirements](#requirements)
- [Getting Started](#getting-started)
- [Frontend](#frontend)
- [Backend](#backend)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [License](#license)

## Features

- User authentication and authorization
- Real-time bidirectional communication using WebSocket
- Chat room functionality with message history
- Responsive UI for various screen sizes

## Requirements

- Node.js and npm installed

